query:
SELECT e.id, e.name, e.fixedDate, e.fixedTime, e.createdAt, COUNT(p.id) as participant_count
FROM events e
LEFT JOIN participants p ON e.id = p.eventId
WHERE e.name = 'Breakfast Meeting'
GROUP BY e.id, e.name, e.fixedDate, e.fixedTime, e.createdAt
ORDER BY e.createdAt;
